20.9.11.name: wordpress/best-seo-itranslator-for-wordpress
20.9.11.description: Best SEO iTranslator for Wordpress is a translation plugin, fully automated, that will help you get new traffic and at the same time help your readers translate your posts in their native languages (from the available 40 languages). This is a perfect SEO instrument for those who want to get traffic from search engines. Best SEO iTranslator for Wordpress generates new translated posts, which are treated by search engines as being new different posts, containing different information.
